OL,6,FLifelong golfer Gordon McLay was
OL,7,Fstruggling to play the game after a
OL,8,Fmotorcycle accident in 2007 and
OL,9,Funderwent a below the knee amputation
OL,10,Ftwo years ago.
OL,12,F"Before my amputation I was playing in
OL,13,Fsevere pain," he said.
OL,15,F"Ever since I've got a new life again
OL,16,FI'm loving it out on the golf course,
OL,17,Fbit of freedom and that's why it's an
OL,18,Fescape from me.
