OL,6,F"When I get on the golf course, I
OL,7,Fdon't think of anything else, I'm just
OL,8,Fthinking about golf.
OL,10,F"Life's strains just disappear."
OL,12,FAdapted equipment such as mobility
OL,13,Fchairs and specially designed clubs
OL,14,Faim to create an equal playing field
OL,15,Ffor athletes with a whole range of
OL,16,Fabilities.
OL,18,FRobbie Clyde, CEO of Scottish Gold
OL,19,Fsaid: "It's really important that we
OL,20,Fshowcase golf as as welcoming and
OL,21,Faccessible for everybody.
